  "title": "高级拉面师",
  "description": "<p>负责拉面餐馆的后厨运营</p>\n<p>懂得如何熬煮兰州牛肉面的原汤</p>\n<p>懂得如何兑汤</p>\n<p>懂得如何熬制兰州牛肉面的油泼辣子</p>\n<p>能熟练制作8种面型</p>\n<p>会炒面，煎鸡肉</p>\n<p>能熟练切牛肉，切蒜苗，白萝卜</p>\n<p>能按公司要求准备小菜</p>\n<p>能做好厨房的清洁工作</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>In charge of the kitchen operation of a Lanzhou Beef Noodle restaurant</p>\n<p>Knowing how to prepare the beef soup</p>\n<p>Knowing how to prepare the chili sauce for Lanzhou Beef Noodle</p>\n<p>Knowing how to pull 8 different types of noodle</p>\n<p>Can fried noodle and grill chicken</p>\n<p>Can cut beef, Chinese Leek and radish efficiently</p>\n<p>Can prepare side dishes according to company's requirement</p>\n<p>Can do cleaning working according to company's requirement</p>",
